E2MF2AU.original: ~z~There's a rich Russian having a pow wow with the old man about you and the fag.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~一个有钱的俄国人正在和老头子商讨你和死基佬的事。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Why the city ain't shut us down, I don't know.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~政府怎么还没关了我们的店？搞不懂。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~I wouldn't miss this. See you there, T.
~z~But if you think about it too long then there might be no getting out of it. Comprende?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~但你想太久的话，可能就没法摆脱困境了。懂了？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Nothing like that. I'm just thinking you could put in some hours at the Maisonette.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~没有的事。只是我希望你能来豪宅看一看。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Yeah. I thought we could persuade him that we're not such bad guys after all.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~对，有必要让他知道我们不是那么糟糕的人。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Time to face the facts, Jack. Frankly, you're fucked.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~你该面对现实了，老兄。真的，你完蛋了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Let's leave your gay club and your homo boss out of this.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~还是先把你的基佬夜店跟男同老板给晾着吧。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~You believed those stories? Wow. I never took you for an idiot. I just pretended to know what I was doing.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~你真的相信那些传说啊？哇哦。没想到你这么傻。我只是装作运筹帷幄而已。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~You have anything to do with a little boating accident that went down and is all over the news?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~那你和现在新闻头条的船难有关系吗？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Doctors' notes don't cut it with these people.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~医疗诊断书对他们可不管用啊。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~But if I had been, it would have been for us, for the business.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~即便我参与了，那也是为了我们，为了生意。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~I been trying to make us some money, yeah.
~z~Troy if it's Hercules, or Luis if it's important. Love you. Bye.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~大力神那边就找Troy，如有急事就找Luis。爱你。拜～

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~I'm real happy, Tone. I'll catch you soon.
~z~Calm shit down, T, and don't take it out on me. I'll be by soon. Take care of yourself.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~冷静点，T，别拿我当出气筒。我会来找你的。你多保重。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Okay, T. Put your feet up. Relax. Enjoy yourself.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~好的，T。你放心吧。好好休息，自己注意。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~I'm a schmuck who got lucky. Shit, we really are screwed!
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~我就是一运气好点的蠢蛋。妈的，这下真完蛋了！

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Hey, Lou. I wanted to say what a good job you been doing with the celebrity clientele. Truly excellent work.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~嘿，Lou。我想好好表扬一下你对名人顾客的处理。干得太棒了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~No! Tony's some out of control shit. Think about what he has got you into.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~不！Tony才是失控的那个。想想他给你惹了多少麻烦。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~No. Yes. No. Sort of. The city's closed down the clubs.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~不。对。不...差不多吧。政府把夜店都关了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~And it turns out the diamonds we bought were stolen off him in the first place.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~结果我们买的钻石似乎是从他那里偷来的。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Yo, man, we already got it. I, ummm, talked to him about some opportunities.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~喂，老兄，已经有压力了。我之前想找他碰碰运气。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~I'll try to put some time in soon, man. Shit's been kind of crazy. Trust me. Look after things.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~我尽量找时间吧，老兄。最近事太多了，真的。有劳你了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~The place could do with that Luis Lopez magic.
~z~Dessie's at Maisonette every night. Just talk to him and he'll explain everything.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~Dessie每晚都在豪宅那边。你问他，他会跟你解释清楚的。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~You been hanging out with people behind my back?
~z~in with the old man seems to want your blood as much as some other parties. I think we need to talk in person.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~他在和头子会面，似乎急着要你的命。我们最好当面谈谈。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~I'm sorry. I fucked up. Kind of refreshing for me to be the one getting us in shit for once, don't you think?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~很抱歉，我搞砸了。这次是我把你拖下水，对我来说还挺新鲜的，不是吗？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Luis, shit, I've been looking for you.
~z~He's bad news. I hate to be the voice of reason here, but I don't think we need that kind of stress in our lives.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~他让我很不舒服。我不想当理中客，但我们不需要他那样的压力。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Thank you, man. It ain't exactly the highlight of my day. They like real people only without the humanity or a sense of humor.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~谢谢夸奖，哥们。其实我也没那么高兴啦。他们喜欢真诚的人，只不过缺少人性和幽默感。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Not so much, Lou. There's this Russian guy
~z~Tony's pissed a lot of people off. You need to control him.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~Tony已经招惹了很多人，你要控制住他。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~No, I'm shitting with you. They were arms smugglers, hitched to some of the worst governments in West Africa.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~不，我骗你的。他们是军火贩子，跟西非的邪恶政权勾结。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Someone told me they saw you driving around with some Russians. What the fuck are they? You gone over to the dark side?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~有人告诉我你跟几个俄国人混在一起，这他妈啥情况？你去混黑社会了？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Hey boss. I'm just wondering when you think you gonna do a shift at the club?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~嘿，老板。你有空的时候能不能来店里当个班？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Alright, let's talk. Come down to the club.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~好啊，谈谈吧。来我们店里谈吧。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~And that's why we love them so. How about this, from now on I can get someone else to handle the VIP shit?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~所以我们才喜欢他们。这样吧，现在开始我找别人负责VIP的事情吧？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~so we can keep these places running. What else you expect me to be doing?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~做混蛋的车夫，这才勉强维持夜店运转。哪有空做别的事？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Rocco's saying we owe him his share of the profits on top of everything else.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~Rocco说他没拿到的钻石分成算我们欠他的。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Good. Because the people on that boat were good people.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~那就好。那条船上可都是大好人。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Too bad, Mex. This line opened up just as soon as Tony took those points.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~太糟了，老墨。Tony拿到钻石以后就给我你的号码了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Meet me and Vincenzo in the public toilets in Middle Park for a two on one.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~我和Vincenzo在中心公园的公厕等你，二对一谈话。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~That Russian gangster? You think he'd lend us the money we need to get out of this shit?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~那个俄国黑帮？你觉得他肯借我们钱摆脱困境？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Besides my life falling apart in front of my eyes, not much is happening... 'bro'.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~我的生活正在眼前崩塌，我还挺好的...「兄弟」。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Rocco, how'd you get my fucking number? I don't want to talk to you.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~Rocco，你哪来的我的号码？我不想听你说话。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~But I had you. I fucking had you. You fucking idiot. Luis. Don't turn into a freedom fighter.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~但我诈到你了。把你诈出来了。你个傻逼，Luis。别当自由斗士了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Okay, okay bro. I'll put in some hours real soon.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~好的好的，兄弟。我会尽快来店里的。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~This ain't good, man, but we'll find a way out of it. You been in worse scrapes before. I'm counting on your leadership.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~情况不妙啊，伙计，不过总会有办法的。更糟糕的情况都挺过来了，我相信你的能力。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Okay, Evan was a conceited dick, a low life, a whore, a drug peddler and a thief.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~好吧，Evan确实是自大狂，是下等人，是淫贼，是毒贩，是小偷。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Listen, Tony, I got something to talk to you about. You remember that Ray Bulgarin guy?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~听着，Tony，我有事要跟你说。还记得那个叫Ray Bulgarin的家伙吗？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Okay. Of course. Shit. The stress is really getting to me.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~好吧，应该是。妈的，我最近压力太大了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~You know, Rock, your guinea ass is lower down this country's ethnic food chain than mine,
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~知道吗，Rock，你的意呆佬血统在美国的种族食物链里比我还低。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Well, what the fuck are me and Tone supposed to do about that?
~z~And they still partying in here... It never ceases to amaze me.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~他们还在这儿狂欢...每次都会让我惊叹。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~I've organized that face-to-face with our good friend the Celebinator.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~我已经安排好和名人终结者这位老朋友的见面了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Standards have slipped, Lou. We're dead without this revenue stream. Just keep an eye on things, okay?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~服务质量差了，Lou。收入流一断就完了。多去店里看看，好吗？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~FYI they ain't talking about handing you a special commendation.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~别搞错了，他们不是打算给你发个什么奖章。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~We don't have the luxury of that right now, and stop going solo on me. Not now.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~我们现在没资本当圣母，也别背着我单干了。暂时先别。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~He treated me like dirt. That's the kind of guy I like.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~他不把我当人看。我就喜欢他这种人。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~I'll be out of town for a while. Don't come looking for me, 'cause you won't find me. I probably ain't gonna check these messages either.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~我最近不在城里。你也不用来找我，找不到我的。大概也不会听语音信箱。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Yo, this is Dessie. Don't call me with any guest list requests, that ain't my department.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~哟，我是Dessie。准入名单相关不要问我，不归我管。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Hey, look, I respect you so I'm gonna talk straight a second.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~喂，听好。出于尊重，我就跟你直说了吧。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Meet me and Uncle Vincenzo in the public toilets in Middle Park. We got to talk in person.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~来中心公园的厕所找我和Vincenzo叔叔。我们得见面谈谈

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~No more ass wiping? That sounds hot.
~z~Dessie, dimelo my man at Maisonette, what's going on?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~Dessie，你好啊，豪宅守门员，店里还好吗？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Oh shit. We gonna show him a good time?
~z~Make sure we're running things to your exacting standards.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~确保我们现在的经营状况符合你的标准。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~are gonna stop expecting envelopes from me because of the homo's midlife crisis?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~会因为这个基佬的中年危机，就不问我要钱了吗？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Luis, what's gotten into you? Why haven't you been helping out at the clubs?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~Luis，你都干啥去了？怎么一直没来店里帮忙？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Really? That's funny, man. Your friend must have been mistaken.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~什么？不是吧，哥们。你朋友认错人了吧。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~If you still want to help Dessie out with the management stuff that's great, but no more celeb whispering.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~如果你还想帮Dessie打理经营方面的事也挺好，但不用处理名人了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Okay. We expected this, Tone. Don't freak out.
~z~He was an asshole. My guess is he was intending to steal them diamonds when the bikers got him.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~他就是个混蛋。我猜他被飞车党抓住的时候，还想着偷钻石。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Let's leave the homo out of this for a minute.
~z~Freedom fighters trying to stop people smuggling in Asia.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~都是想要阻止亚洲人贩子的自由斗士。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~We better do it quick. There's no more money coming in.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~那要速战速决，我们的收入来源断了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~You should start going back to the shrink, bro.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~你该回去找心理医生看看了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~It's only gonna get worse for us. Fuck me I need some blow.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~越拖情况越糟。操了，我想吸点粉。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~The place never runs as smooth as when you're on site.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~你当班的时候，店里的状态才是最好的。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Same old, boss. But we could do with your input.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~还是老样子，老板。如果你能来就再好不过了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Yo, D. There ain't been a disaster has there?
~z~He's meeting us at the Heliport on the West River - we're taking him out on a tour of the city.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~他会在西河的停机坪跟我们碰头，待会儿让他见识下自由城的风光。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~He cut that cook's head off. Long story short he wants us dead.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~他还把那个厨子的头砍了。简而言之，他要我们死。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~What could you possibly have to say that I'd want to hear, Rock?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~你嘴里能不能蹦出一点我爱听的话，Rock？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~I know you can handle it, bro. But if you want me there, I'll come by.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~我相信你的能力，兄弟。不过你想要我来的话，我会来的。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Screw you. Anyway, that doesn't solve the diamond issue.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~去你妈的。总之，钻石的事还没结束。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Be reasonable then, Rock. Chinatown? Bahama Mama's? Those fucking bombs? That's some out of control shit, man.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~差不多得了，Rock。唐人街？巴哈马妈妈？那几次爆破？都是些失控的活计。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Have you heard the news? Evan's definitely dead.
~z~Really? I heard they was... shit... I heard...
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~什么？我听说他们是...妈的...我听说...

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~You serious? I been running round this city getting shot at by assholes, doing hits for assholes, and hanging out with assholes,
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~没搞错吧？我在城里到处挨混蛋的枪子，干混蛋的脏活，

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Look at my position, it's some serious moula he owes. You think the higher powers
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~以我的立场来说，他欠的可是一笔巨款。你以为上面的人

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Shit, T. Maybe this is a good thing. At least we can concentrate on getting off every gangster's hit list.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~妈的，T。说不定这样也好，至少我们可以专心应付黑帮的追杀了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~I can't believe these guy is still going?
~z~Poor old chef. What were you doing talking to these guys without me, Lou?
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~可怜的老厨子。你和这些人交涉怎么不带上我，Lou？

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~This is Tony. You haven't gotten hold of me, so give Dessie a call if this is concerning Maisonette,
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~我是Tony，现在听不了电话。豪宅方面的事情请找Dessie，

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Cause that will put a real hetero spin on proceedings? Sure.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~因为这样不会显得那么基情？好吧。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~All this fucking bullshit and we forgot to pay off the Citadel.
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~忙活了半天，结果忘记打点市政厅了。

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Tony's gonna calm down as soon as you stop sending us on suicide missions!
E2MF2AU.translated: ~z~你不给我们整这些自杀任务，Tony自然会冷静下来的！

E2MF2AU.original: ~z~Yo, it's the Rock. Leave a message.
